Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.63,0:22:52.72,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}使用自己的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.85,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一定是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:00.85,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}以這扭曲的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.40,0:23:03.90,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}制訂萬無一失的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.15,0:23:08.15,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我將馬上前往去迎接你的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.15,0:23:09.74,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}請等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.78,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}即使這是不可能的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.83,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}也會用盡想像力克服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.49,0:23:18.58,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}要是一不小心陷入僵局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.88,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那時候便去隨機應變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:25.09,Ending - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}本應是一無所有的我們
